The Mambo Kings;;1992;;R;;Drama,Music;;6.4;;Arne Glimcher;;Armand Assante,Antonio Banderas,Pablo Calogero,Scott Cohen,Mario Grillo,Ralph Irizarry,Pete Macnamara,James Medina,Marcos Quintanilla,J.T. Taylor,William Thomas Jr.,Yul Vazquez,Cathy Moriarty,Maruschka Detmers,Desi Arnaz Jr.,Celia Cruz,Roscoe Lee Browne,Vondie Curtis-Hall;;Musician brothers Cesar and Nestor leave Cuba for America in the 1950s, hoping to hit the top of the Latin music scene. Cesar is the older brother, the business manager, and the ladies' man. Nestor is the brooding songwriter, who cannot forget the woman in Cuba who broke his heart.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0104802/